I've noticed, you cheeky little thing!


* Iron Raptor simply sighed.*

" I can take care of myself, Prowl. Believe it or not, I don't need you 
tagging along with me everywhere."

* She didn't mean to sound rude but this kinda made her feel almost as if he 
didn't trust her to look after herself anymore.
Looking back she noticed him swooping down a bit, wondering just what it was 
he was up to...but it didn't matter. The treeline was only a few hundred 
meters from her position now.*
